---
/**
 * About Section with Timeline and Values
 */
---

<section class="relative w-full py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-surface to-primary/5">
  <!-- Decorative Elements -->
  <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-80 h-80 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide">
        ðŸ“– Our Story
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-content">
        Made with Love & Laughter
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-content-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        From a small kitchen dream to your favorite donut shop
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Story Text -->
      <div class="space-y-6 animate-fade-in-left">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-lg text-content-light leading-relaxed">
            What started as a weekend project in 2020 has blossomed into a beloved community bakery. We were inspired by the joy and mischief of our favorite yellow characters, and we wanted to bring that same happiness to everyone's breakfast table.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-content-light leading-relaxed">
            Every single donut is handcrafted with premium ingredients, zero artificial flavors, and lots of love. We believe that life is too short for mediocre donuts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Values Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-6">
          {[
            { icon: "ðŸ¥š", title: "Fresh Ingredients", desc: "Sourced daily from local suppliers" },
            { icon: "ðŸ¤", title: "Community First", desc: "Supporting local causes and events" },
            { icon: "âœ¨", title: "Quality Always", desc: "No shortcuts, only excellence" },
            { icon: "ðŸŒ±", title: "Sustainable", desc: "Eco-friendly packaging & practices" }
          ].map((value, index) => (
            <div
              class="group p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-outline/20 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer hover:-translate-y-1 animate-fade-in-up"
              style={`animation-delay: ${300 + index * 100}ms`}
            >
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">{value.icon}</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-content mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">{value.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-content-light">{value.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Timeline/Milestones -->
      <div class="space-y-8 animate-fade-in-right">
        <div class="relative">
          {/* Timeline Line */}
          <div class="absolute left-6 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary via-secondary to-accent"></div>

          {/* Timeline Items */}
          {[
            { year: "2020", title: "The Beginning", desc: "First batch baked in a home kitchen" },
            { year: "2021", title: "Grand Opening", desc: "Opened our first brick-and-mortar shop" },
            { year: "2022", title: "Community Love", desc: "Reached 1,000 happy customers" },
            { year: "2024", title: "Expansion", desc: "Multi-location growth & online ordering" }
          ].map((milestone, index) => (
            <div
              class="relative pl-24 pb-8 group cursor-pointer animate-fade-in-up"
              style={`animation-delay: ${500 + index * 100}ms`}
            >
              {/* Timeline Dot */}
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-14 h-14 bg-white border-4 border-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-primary group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                {milestone.year.slice(-2)}
              </div>

              {/* Content Card */}
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline/20 group-hover:border-primary/50 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-1">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-content group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-1">
                  {milestone.title}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-content-light">{milestone.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fade-in-left {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-40px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fade-in-right {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(40px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .animate-fade-in-left {
    animation: fade-in-left 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-fade-in-right {
    animation: fade-in-right 0.6s ease-out;
  }
</style>
